<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Supplementary description.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Female genitalia</emphasis>
. Tergite IX (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figure 2. Betacixius flagellihamus Zhang &amp; Chen, 2011, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439747" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">2A, B, D</figureCitation>
) moderately sclerotized, with a large nearly dumbbell-shaped wax plate. Anal segment (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figure 2. Betacixius flagellihamus Zhang &amp; Chen, 2011, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439747" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">2C</figureCitation>
) rectangular, widening to apex, 1.5 times wider than long in dorsal view, anal style strap-like. Gonapophysis VIII (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figure 2. Betacixius flagellihamus Zhang &amp; Chen, 2011, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439747" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">2E</figureCitation>
) elongate, and slightly curved upwards. Gonapophysis IX (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figure 2. Betacixius flagellihamus Zhang &amp; Chen, 2011, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439747" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">2F</figureCitation>
) with two middle teeth, distance ratio between distal middle tooth to apex and length of denticulate portion is 2.1. Gonoplac (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figure 2. Betacixius flagellihamus Zhang &amp; Chen, 2011, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439747" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">2G</figureCitation>
) rod-like, 3.6 times longer than wide in lateral view. Posterior vagina pattern as shown in Figure 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 2" captionStartId="F2" captionText="Figure 2. Betacixius flagellihamus Zhang &amp; Chen, 2011, female A genitalia, lateral view B genitalia, ventral view C anal segment, dorsal view D tergite IX, caudal view E gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, ventral view F gonapophysis IX, lateral view G gonoplac, inner lateral view H posterior vagina, ventral view I posterior vagina, dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.956.50195.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/439747" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">2H, I</figureCitation>
.
</paragraph>
